title: Tori Spelling

description:
Hollywood legend Tori Spelling is the guest this week and it's a W I L D one.  Tori and Whitney discuss psych meds, fake boobs, and fish-hooking.  Tori brings her albino hedgehogs and Whitney brings cheap rosé.  Watch Tori on MESSYNESS on MTV and listen to her podcast 90210MG out every Monday.
